If Win 95 had been too good, then no one would migrate to NT.

I predicted many, many months ago that Win 95 was not gonna be *too*
successful running Win 3.x applications, because if it were, then you
wouldn't upgrade your *apps*, now wouldja? And anyway, Borland, Symantec
