very nice advantage for the Home Team, eh?

Nudge nudge, wink wink, know what I mean?

Prediction: Win 96 or whatever the hell they call it will probably be
a better, more stable and less buggy version of Win 95 in all respects
EXCEPT ONE: it will not run Win 3.x apps AS WELL AS Win 95.

